text: The Logan, also known as El Beudor or the Sherwyn Hotel, is a historic building in Omaha, Nebraska. It was built in 1918, and designed by architect James T. Allan. With It has been listed on the National Register of Historic Places since July 22, 2005. ==References== Category:National Register of Historic Places in Omaha, Nebraska Category:Early Commercial architecture in the United States Category:Commercial buildings completed in 1918 Category:1918 establishments in Nebraska
title: The Logan (Omaha, Nebraska)
